Lambda@Edge allows you to run Lambda functions to customise content that CloudFront delivers - with execution occuring closer to the user.

Lambda functions can be used to changeCloudFront requests and responses:

 - after CloudFront receives a request form a viewer
 - Before CF receives a request to the origin
 - Afrer CF forwards the request to the origin
 - Before CF forwards response to the viewer
 
 
 
