 API Gateway provides throttling at multiple levels (global, by a service call), limits can be set for standard rates and bursts
 
 API owners can set a rate limit of 1000 requests oer second for a specific method in REST APIs, and configure API Gateway to handle a burst of 2000 req per soc for a few seconds
 
 any requests over the API Gateway limit will recieve 429 HTTP response
 
 
